sources.title: Pals of the Range (1935) REX LEASE
sources.description:
1st TIME on YouTube!
Stars: Rex Lease, Frances Morris, Yakima Canutt
Director: Elmer Clifton

A cowboy goes after cattle rustlers he finds changing brands.

metadata.Plot: Returning to help his old pal 'Dust', Steve runs into cattle rustlers changing brands. He starts bringing them in one at a time but when Zed shoots his boss Tom, the Sheriff arrives to arrest Steve. But Steve and the Sheriff are old friends and when the Sheriff lets him go, Steve heads out to bring in Zed, the boss of the gang.
metadata.Actors: Rex Lease, Frances Morris, Yakima Canutt
